Notice how smoking has this protective function in a community. Neighbors were outside on their porch smoking and were able to come help. When there are smokers there's always someone outside even at night to keep an eye out on what's going on around. Makes everyone safer overall

Even in urban areas with apartment buildings there's always someone smoking over a window or sitting on the balcony looking down who would see someone getting mugged on the street etc. and be able to call the cops or yell out. Every smoker is a hobbyist night-guard keeping watch.
